                  Allen J. Whang, Chi-Kuei Chung, “Accurate interference pattern analysis module of automatic measurement system,” Optica Applicata, Vol. 33, No. 4 (2003) pp. 627-634              




會議



              	[1]              

                 “A Y-branch light collecting device for natural light guiding system” Kuan-Yu Chen, Yi-Yung Chen, Jr-Chia Chiang, and Allen Jong-Woei Whang Proc. SPIE 7717, 77171E (2010)               



              	[2]              

                 “Design and measurement of TIR lens of MR16-compatible LED lamp without aspherical surface for high directivity” Wei-Che Hsieh, Yi-Yung Chen, Yu-Chi Lee, and Allen Jong-Woei Whang Proc. SPIE 7717, 771714 (2010)               



              	[3]              

                 “The design of optical module of LED street lamp with non-axial symmetrical reflector”Ming-Jun Lu, Chi-An Chen, Yi-Yung Chen, and Allen Jong-Woei Whang Proc. SPIE 7717, 771713 (2010)               



