                 “Design and optimization of automotive headlamps based on projection system with double ellipsoidal reflector” Chi-Tang Ma, Kao-Hsu Chou, Yi-Yung Chen, Allen Jong-Woei Whang, and Kuan-Yu Chen Proc. SPIE 7717, 77170M (2010)               



              	[5]              

